oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Formicola Morning Show Highlights - Joe Wade - WWWW
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Excerpts from radio show Formicola-In-The-Morning, featuring Joe Wade (host), broadcast on radio station WWWW [W4] (Detroit, Mich.)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: (00:00) [Unidentified] introduces Joe Wade's Formicola-In-The-Morning -- (00:23) Joe Wade calls a listener at 5 AM -- (00:45) Joe Wade talks about an Elvis sighting in Kalamazoo at a Burger King -- Wade calls the Burger King -- (04:03) Joe Wade reports live at a pet show as a comedy routine -- (05:13) Wade talks about a friend chicken restaurant giving leftover chicken to their employees, and the health department cracking down on it, then Wade sings a jingle -- (07:05) Comedy skit of a couple attending a Mike Tyson fight -- (07:45) Closing statements for Formicola-In-The-Morning with advertisement
